---
// HowItWorks.astro - 4 steps: Sign up, Start Learning, Weekly Calls, Keep Growing
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 bg-gray-50 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background decoration -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none opacity-40">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 -left-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-100 rounded-full filter blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 -right-20 w-64 h-64 bg-violet-100 rounded-full filter blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-animate">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        How It Works
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4">
        From learning to code to landing your first software engineering role â€” here's how we'll get you there.
      </p>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-violet-600 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connection line - hidden on mobile, visible on lg -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-24 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-200 via-violet-200 to-blue-200" style="top: 4rem;"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Step 1: Career Assessment -->
        <div class="text-center group h-full scroll-animate">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 h-full flex flex-col relative card-elevated">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg relative z-10">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Career Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              We'll discuss your background, career goals, and current situation. Together, we'll create a personalized roadmap tailored to your specific needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Learn & Build -->
        <div class="text-center group h-full scroll-animate">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 h-full flex flex-col relative card-elevated">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500 to-violet-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg relative z-10">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 w-8 h-8 bg-violet-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-violet-600">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Learn & Build</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              Start building real projects for your portfolio with my guidance. Get code reviews and learn industry best practices as you develop your skills.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Weekly Support -->
        <div class="text-center group h-full scroll-animate">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 h-full flex flex-col relative card-elevated">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-violet-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg relative z-10">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 w-8 h-8 bg-violet-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-violet-600">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Weekly Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              Regular one-on-one sessions to review progress, debug issues, and stay motivated. Get answers to your questions and overcome obstacles.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Land the Job -->
        <div class="text-center group h-full scroll-animate">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 h-full flex flex-col relative card-elevated">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg relative z-10">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-green-600">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Land the Job</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              Polish your portfolio, practice interviews, and navigate the job search process. Get ongoing support until you land your first engineering role.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16 scroll-animate">
      <button
        onclick="if(window.trackCTAClick) window.trackCTAClick('how_it_works_begin'); document.getElementById('signup').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'});"
        class="btn-primary bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl cursor-pointer"
      >
        Begin Your Journey
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
